videos.description: UCLA's Isaac Hamilton sets up Lonzo Ball for a two-handed alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Ball with early highlight alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Washington State takes its first lead of the second half off Josh Hawkinson's hook shot.
videos.headline: Washington State still hanging around in the 2nd half

videos.description: UCLA's Ike Anigbogu rejects Washington State's Robert Franks on his dunk attempt.
videos.headline: Anigbogu protects the rim with ferocious block

videos.description: Lonzo Ball's father, LaVar Ball, discusses his thoughts on critics of Lonzo's shooting form and says Lonzo has a "big, baller, backyard shot."
videos.headline: Ball's father defends son's shot

videos.description: UCLA guard Bryce Alford explains what his emotions were like during senior night and why he believes the Bruins being assessed a No. 3 seed in the NCAA tournament is not fair.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Not fair for UCLA to be assessed a 3 seed) 2017/03/04 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Not fair for UCLA to be assessed a 3 seed

videos.description: Lonzo Ball scores 12 points and dishes out 14 assists as the No. 3 Bruins roll pass the Cougars 77-68 to finish the regular season 28-3.
videos.headline: Ball drops double-double in UCLA's win
